    AROcclusionManager could cause some objects to become incorrectly occluded for
    ARCore and ARKit apps.\n- Fixed `LoaderUtility` so that it correctly initializes
    or deinitializes the OpenXR Loader when you call `Initialize` or `Deinitialize`,
    respectfully.\n- Fixed the following methods of [XRBoundingBox](xref:UnityEngine.XR.ARSubsystems.XRBoundingBox):\n 
